            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "Hey @0xbadc0de, @DasIch is right. [Builtin function `apply`](http://docs.python.org/2/library/functions.html#apply) [has been removed in Python 3](http://docs.python.org/3.3/whatsnew/3.0.html#builtins). This is an [acknowledged  bug in PyOpenSSL](https://bugs.launchpad.net/pyopenssl/+bug/1211834). Please close this.\n"
